        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Regen is very important if you try to play efficient.<BR>Vexing is very inefficient DoT.</P><P>Its all about your play style really.</P><P>HP = more room for error, FT / Regen = more efficient killing.<BR>What would you rather have? 3000hp 0 ft 0 regen or 2000hp FT15 +15regen. (i know this are extreme examples but still)</P><P>In first case you will survive more yes, in second case you'll "do" more over time.<BR>Its up to you to choose what you want, but a high skilled player with more FT / regen will ALWAYS outdo someone with more HP but lower FT / regen over time.</P><P></P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
