         I was fairly certain that Angrier was trolling the serverwide chat when he was going on and on about this FT gear thing for necros, now I'm convinced he actually believes it.</P><P>Although the reasons HP is the best thing for a necro - Angrier and his ideas about flowing thought will still exist.  It's a huge error in your thinking Angrier, that is all.</P><P>Regen is, without a doubt, the most important thing to a necro.  Had I learned of this a year ago, I'd have rolled an Iksar.  Following regen closely is HP.  FT really doesn't even come into the picture at ALL.  I have FT 5 and would trade it all for 50hp without a hesitation.  I got these FT items for the HP on them, not the FT - so you could say i got the best of both worlds.  FT 5 is 50 mana per MINUTE.  I get more than that using AL in 2 ticks.  If I traded my FT 5 for 50hp, that is almost the entire 2 ticks (counting in regen) paid for giving me more mana in 1/5th of the time.  Now utilizing this more mana bestowed upon me from my HP, I cast dots, when low HP I cast another DOT that actually HEALS me TOO!</P><P>I play on a pvp server, so I have many other concerns than HP alone, but if I were playing on a blue server, you can bet your ass I'd have xp gear that was completely HP.</P><P>You can have 2 necro's with exact same stats INT wise and Regen wise, one in HP gear and one with mana gear test this out very easily.  Just see who can keep going the longest on an xp spot.</P><P>Of course, pre BOD you just might have a point that mana > HP for xp.  I'm talking post 50 and even moreso post Vexxing.</P><P>I do however wish you the best of luck in your quest for mana and FT gear.  I'm sure you prefer to use KEI whenever you can also.  Which reminds me of a lvl 44+ necro in OT the other day (I know this, he DMF'd my chanter) who kept coming to me for clarity.  ?  WTF is a lvl 44 Necro doing using CLARITY for crying out loud. And he'd be right back as soon as it wore off - is this how you xp Angrier? With clarity, C2 or KEI?  That would help me realize how you cant understand the HP concept.</P><P>Fermunda <Hate> </P><P>Sullon Zek</P><P>Edited by - Fermunda on 09/30/2002  13:40:23<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
